    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change the legal age to buy and consume alcohol to 16",
        "additional_details": "16-year-olds can go into the army, work and contribute to the economy. We think it\u2019s only fair they get the same privileges 18-year-olds do.\r\n \r\nWe believe it could also boost the economy with more people contributing to small businesses.\r\n",
        "background": "Make the legal drinking age 16 in public places like bars and clubs. Make the legal age to purchase alcohol from shops 16 too.",
